features: All-in-One Bulk Pack: This pack includes 12 pastel colored highlighters, 6 adorable mechanical pencils, 5 black ink gel pens, 5 gel pen refills, a charming pink pencil pouch, 3 jelly erasers, 9 cap erasers, and 6 tubes of lead refills. It's the ultimate collection of multifunctional stationery essentials for office and school supplies.

Large Pencil Pouch with Supplies: This expandable pencil pouch boasts a big storage capacity with four compartments for orderly organization. Crafted from a soft, tactile material, it is not only waterproof and durable but also comfortable to handle. The smoothly operating zipper ensures hassle-free access to your supplies.

5 PCS Retractable Gel Pens: Enjoy smooth writing with these fine point gel pens that feature a comfortable grip and a balanced, weighted spring for a low center of gravity sensation. The pen clip prevents paper damage, and the quick-drying ink lets you write neatly without smears or stains—perfect for journaling and note-taking. Plus, it comes with 5 extra refills for enduring use.

12 Assorted Colors Highlighters: These neutral, colorful markers are gentle on the eyes while adding just the right amount of vibrancy. The versatile chisel tip makes it simple to switch between fine and bold strokes. The durable, not easy to bleed ink keeps pages crisp and clear.

6PCS Mechanical Pencils Set for Artists: This set includes 3 pencils with 0.5mm leads, 3 with 0.7mm leads, 6 tubes of #2 lead refills, 3 jelly erasers, and 9 cap eraser refills. The ergonomic triangular grip fosters a comfortable hold, ensuring a pleasant writing and drawing experience. Note: This set is suitable for children over 3 years old.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful and good quality! I got this to have a good variety of pencils and pens I can keep in my bag for school that are also cute. Highly recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My son loves this set! The bag is very nice and expandable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice Set; Great Pen Case!
reviews.reviewText: I actually chose these as additions to my new crafting studio as I was looking for a set of pens with a variety of inks & in a case I could easily "grab & go" with as I moved around my studio or traveled as I am constantly creating, sketching, designing things whether on an airplane, at a family reunion, or working in my tricked-out studio. My only disappointment with this set is a few of the pens were difficult to get the ink started (like maybe pens were fairly old) & one pen completely didn't work at all. Still, the set is worth the money in my opinion &, bonus -- my 5 year old project loving grandson decided he wanted to use the pens & is now practicing his writing in both English & Chinese (he's in the Chinese immersion program here) now that he has "cool pencils" to use to write with!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for office supplies
reviews.reviewText: Love this set for my work day! I work from home and use these everyday and help me finish my normal 8-5 workday! Definitely worth it!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this and was not sent the full set. A mini version of it arrived with no markers, no bag, and other items missing as well. I requested a replacement, and again received the wrong set. It was labeled correctly both times, but the sets I received were had about 1/3 of the listed items. Frustrating. I can’t speak to the quality as my issue with paying for a full set and receiving twice an inadequate one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Had missing items
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I was very excited about this item. Thinking it would be an all in one from me returning to school. I only received the pencils, erasers, and lead in a plastic container. Very disappointed!Edit. They mailed me out a new complete set. And I am very pleased with this product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not worth it
reviews.reviewText: For $30 this is not worth it.It has been in my possession for days and th fabric on the pencil pouch has a foul smell that will not go away.The pens are dark black ink, but they do not dry down fast causing the ink to smear almost instantly.The pencils felt nice.The highlighters were not normal pastel or neon colors. Some were dark grey, dark pink, colors that could cross out whatever you are highlighting because they were so dark.All in all for $30 it was not worth it and I well be returning.I like the pencils though and already own some from this brand so I will just stick to liking their pencils.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: For $25 you’d think you’d get okay quality but this stuff is made super cheaply

Super disappointed that 3/4’s of the highlighters are dried out and don’t work. The pens are awesome which is why I’m giving it 2 stars but super sad about the highlighters especially considering it was $30Edit: they sent me a new pack without telling me! So I appreciate that very much :)
